  "text": "Discovery [CITATION_1] ) is another dataset for discourse marker prediction, composed of 174 discourse markers with 20k usage examples for each marker. Sentence pairs were extracted from web data, and the markers come either from the PDTB or from an heuristic automatic extraction. We finetune BERT on the STILTs with 1 to 3 epoch and select the best performing model according to DiscEval average development set accuracy.",
